Z","msg":"佢之前係咪投資香港電影失利搞到間公司即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b69cd192e5c33bd65685dc75a10623fead560ede","tid":597180,"uid":106336,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"600d5e0393870cfa81bf322bae0b6d1a587c8de9","tid":597180,"uid":53855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"佢之前係咪投資香港電影失利搞到間公司即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1991年劉德華創立天幕製作有限公司，他從演員轉型為幕後投資者，是希望擁有自己的電影公司，可以幫助他拍攝更多不同類型的影片，也圓他的電影夢。起初經營頗為成功，也賺到不少錢。後期，因天幕經營失敗令劉德華虧損4000多萬港幣。2000年麥紹棠以上市公司中建電訊名義注資天幕公司，劉德華簽約成為天幕公司旗下藝人。<br />\n中建電訊更向法院申請禁制令，全面封殺劉德華為其他公司做唱片、接拍影視和廣告等演出機會，等於全面封殺劉的演藝事業，結果禁制令成功，使得劉德華在禁制令生效期間估計損失收入上億元。[112]最終雙方在麗新集團老闆林建岳的調停下達成和解協議[262]。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF#%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%A7%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%258F%25AF%23%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25BA%25A7%25E9%2598%25B6%25E6%25AE%25B5&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7509d275\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF#%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%A7%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢搞成咁都仲咁支持港產片<br />\n抵佢咁多人鐘意"},{"pid":"292b5532d6a83497d6403aea725387dcb2425b3b","tid":597180,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa0597f9a751e0eaeb2a1b5ac0fd09163b11084","tid":597180,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"踩港產片個班明星正一雜種狗<br />\n又唔諗自己係邊到紅起<img src=\"